I cursed her under my
breath. while every day

488
00:29:47.936 --> 00:29:50.687
I thanked God for allowing
me to wash my hands of her.

489
00:29:51.757 --> 00:29:52.923
of Toledo.

490
00:29:55.794 --> 00:29:57.060
all of it. I...

491
00:29:59.564 --> 00:30:01.164
So I ran home

492
00:30:02.334 --> 00:30:03.500
to Judy

493
00:30:05.104 --> 00:30:06.803
and I buried the secret.

494
00:30:09.274 --> 00:30:11.207
But I never got a chance

495
00:30:13.078 --> 00:30:15.411
to bury my... my son.

496
00:30:28.460 --> 00:30:30.727
What kind of a
person does that. Ben?

497
00:30:31.730 --> 00:30:33.730
Sacrifices somebody else's life

498
