stack of Bibles. whatever it takes.

509
00:31:01.977 --> 00:31:04.377
Wait. what did you say
the docket number was?

510
00:31:05.247 --> 00:31:08.131
It's. uh. 296-SPE.

511
00:31:08.200 --> 00:31:09.511
Oh.

512
00:31:09.535 --> 00:31:10.695
What's wrong?

513
00:31:10.736 --> 00:31:12.496
Come with me.

514
00:31:17.893 --> 00:31:20.460
